#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn35.145"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn35.145:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 35 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 35 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.145:0.2"
msgid "14. Devadahavagga "
msgstr "14. At Devadaha "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 145. Bāhirānattahetusutta → bāhiraanattasuttaṃ (bj) | hetunā bāhira 3 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn35.145:0.3"
msgid "145. Bāhirānattahetusutta "
msgstr "145. Exterior and Cause Are Not-Self "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.132, sc1
msgctxt "sn35.145:1.1"
msgid "“Rūpā, bhikkhave, anattā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, sights are not-self. "

msgctxt "sn35.145:1.2"
msgid "Yopi hetu, yopi paccayo rūpānaṃ uppādāya, sopi anattā. "
msgstr "The cause and condition that gives rise to sights is also not-self. "

msgctxt "sn35.145:1.3"
msgid "Anattasambhūtā, bhikkhave, rūpā kuto attā bhavissanti. "
msgstr "Since sights are produced by what is not-self, how could they be self? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.145:1.4"
msgid "Saddā … "
msgstr "Sounds … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.145:1.5"
msgid "gandhā … "
msgstr "Smells … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.145:1.6"
msgid "rasā … "
msgstr "Tastes … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.145:1.7"
msgid "phoṭṭhabbā … "
msgstr "Touches … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.145:1.8"
msgid "dhammā anattā. "
msgstr "Thoughts are not-self. "

msgctxt "sn35.145:1.9"
msgid "Yopi hetu, yopi paccayo dhammānaṃ uppādāya, sopi anattā. "
msgstr "The cause and condition that gives rise to thoughts is also not-self. "

msgctxt "sn35.145:1.10"
msgid "Anattasambhūtā, bhikkhave, dhammā kuto attā bhavissanti. "
msgstr "Since thoughts are produced by what is not-self, how could they be self? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.145:1.11"
msgid "Evaṃ passaṃ, bhikkhave, sutavā ariyasāvako rūpesupi nibbindati, saddesupi … gandhesupi … rasesupi … phoṭṭhabbesupi … dhammesupi nibbindati. "
msgstr "Seeing this … "

msgctxt "sn35.145:1.12"
msgid "Nibbindaṃ virajjati; virāgā vimuccati; vimuttasmiṃ vimuttamiti ñāṇaṃ hoti. "
msgstr "Being disillusioned, desire fades away. When desire fades away they’re freed. When they’re freed, they know they’re freed. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.145:1.13"
msgid "‘Khīṇā jāti, vusitaṃ brahmacariyaṃ, kataṃ karaṇīyaṃ, nāparaṃ itthattāyā’ti pajānātī”ti. "
msgstr "They understand: ‘Rebirth is ended, the spiritual journey has been completed, what had to be done has been done, there is no return to any state of existence.’” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.145:1.14"
msgid "Dvādasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.145:1.15"
msgid "Devadahavaggo catuttho. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn35.145:2.1"
msgid "Devadaho khaṇo rūpā, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn35.145:2.2"
msgid "dve natumhākameva ca; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn35.145:2.3"
msgid "Hetunāpi tayo vuttā, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn35.145:2.4"
msgid "duve ajjhattabāhirāti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
